---
import Container from "@/components/Container.astro";
---

<Container class="grid max-w-4xl gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 md:gap-12">
  <h2>This is <span class="text-accent">not</span> a dating event</h2>
  <div class="md:col-span-2">
    <p class="mb-4">
      We'll be stepping into roles and trying out behaviors we might never do in
      real life. We'll do things that push our edges and make us uncomfortable.
      We'll say &ldquo;yes&rdquo; to things we might normally say &ldquo;hell
      no&rdquo; to, and vice versa. We might even say things that would get us
      slapped in a different context.
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="font-semibold"
        >If you feel a new spark with someone during the event,</span
      > we ask that rather than sharing it with them directly, you contact the organizers
      after the event when we send out feedback forms. We can then connect you with
      that person if they are also interested. This helps maintain the playful, pressure-free
      environment of the event and ensures that everyone can fully engage in the activities
      without worrying about judgement or expectations.
    </p>
  </div>
</Container>
